reviewText: The one reason to check this disk out, imho, is that there is a nice strip tease by former Playboy Playmate Ava Fabian at the beginning.  Not a bad scene for Ava fans!  As others have said, the rest of the disk is very ordinary.
this video is horrible. women are very beautful, but is extremely boring. might as well get a sports illistrated because that is about as much nudity as this will give you. Rachel's Angels
